OL,4,Csentenced for terror offences
OL,6,FA police officer who shared images
OL,7,Fsupporting Hamas has been sentenced
OL,8,Ffor terror offences.
OL,10,FMohammed Adil, who was serving with
OL,11,FWest Yorkshire Police in Bradford at
OL,12,Fthe time, pleaded guilty to sharing
OL,13,Ftwo images, along with text, which
OL,14,Fshowed support for the Palestinian
OL,15,Fmilitant group.
OL,17,FThe Independent Officer for Police
OL,18,FConduct (IOPC) investigated after Adil
OL,19,Fwas reported by two colleagues before
OL,20,Fthe case was transferred to the Crown
OL,21,FProsecution Service (CPS).
